Custom function to initialize all output channels.

simplesect.title: Description
simplesect.para: This function is called once at initialization and allows the custom layer to provide specific functionality to initialize internal objects.

simplesect.title: Assumptions, External Events, and Notes:
simplesect.para: This function must be defined, but not all custom layers will do anything in this function.

briefdescription.para: Custom function to initialize custom event filters.

simplesect.title: Description
simplesect.para: This function is called once at initialization and sets the event filters for custom layer EID's if necessary. Passed the index of the first empty entry of TO_AppData.EventTbl. Should be called in TO_InitEvent().

simplesect.title: Assumptions, External Events, and Notes:
simplesect.para: This function must be defined, but not all custom layers will do anything in this function. ind assumed to be between 0 and CFE_MAX_EVENT_FILTERS, and point to an unused location in TO_AppData.EventTbl.

parameterdescription.para: Pointer to a value the will be used for size of the EventTbl array to register TO event messages for filtering

briefdescription.para: Custom function to build up all output channels.

simplesect.title: Description
simplesect.para: This function is called after a new configuration table has been loaded, allowing the custom layer to do whatever it needs to do after a reconfiguration, if anything.

simplesect.title: Assumptions, External Events, and Notes:
simplesect.para: This function must be defined, but not all custom layers will do anything in this function.

briefdescription.para: Custom function in to tear down all output channels.

simplesect.title: Description
simplesect.para: This function is called in preparation for loading a new configuration table, allowing the custom layer to do whatever it needs with the current configuration before reconfiguration, if anything.

simplesect.title: Assumptions, External Events, and Notes:
simplesect.para: This function must be defined, but not all custom layers will do anything in this function.

briefdescription.para: Custom function to cleanup all output channels before shutdown.

simplesect.title: Description
simplesect.para: This function is called in preparation for application shutdown. This allows the custom layer to do whatever it needs to do, if anything.

simplesect.title: Assumptions, External Events, and Notes:
simplesect.para: This function must be defined, but not all custom layers will do anything in this function.

briefdescription.para: Custom function to process new commands.

simplesect.title: Description
simplesect.para: This function is called when the sealed layer receives a command it doesn't know about. This allows the custom layer to receive commands without requiring the sealed layer to know about it.

simplesect.title: Assumptions, External Events, and Notes:
simplesect.para: This function must be defined, though not all custom layers will have commands to process. This function must at least raise an event when an unknown command is received.

parameterdescription.para: A CFE_SB_Msg_t pointer that references the software bus message

briefdescription.para: Custom function to return channel mode status.

simplesect.title: Description
simplesect.para: This function returns the status of a channel from the custom layer.

simplesect.title: Assumptions, External Events, and Notes:
simplesect.para: This function must be defined, though not all custom layers will have commands to process. This function must at least raise an event when an unknown command is received.

parameterdescription.para: The channel to return the status of
